dk.dtu.sb.spn
Class RateFunction

java.lang.Object
  dk.dtu.sb.spn.RateFunction

public class RateFunction
extends java.lang.Object

Holds a mathematical formula describing the rate of a Reaction. Basically this is just a wrapper of a Calculable-object, where the unknown variables can be changed at runtime.

getRate

public double getRate(java.util.Map<java.lang.String,java.lang.Integer> vars)
If calc is not set we assume the constantRate is used. Else the variables in calc is set to the values given in the vars parameter.

Parameters:
vars - A map with the current values of the variables.
Returns:
The rate calculated or the constantRate.
